:"2016-12-25T09:59:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>幾錢人工？做幾耐先可以上$20000<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n新入職12000<br />\n夠2年15000<br />\n升到3柴就有20000⬆️</blockquote><br />\n係撚萬2<br />\n我未3個月都就出緊萬3幾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f48ea59789f6b74da45d2145a984f7ac80eecf64","tid":54081,"uid":7021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T10:26:11.000Z","msg":"做到最大職級有幾錢人工一個月"},{"pid":"275eb0cafb9952de45d0d336009694490c527feb","tid":54081,"uid":60810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T10:27:25.000Z","msg":"點入職？"},{"pid":"18466b937f79bc3b9eff1580d379ac6f079dd478","tid":54081,"uid":9683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T10:51:05.000Z","msg":"點apply? 上鴨屎綠avseco 個網到apply就得<br />\n<br />\n有手有腳就請，腦都唔使用<br />\n<br />\n入到去要上7日堂，個7日唔計你人工，幫你考個食q牌<br />\n<br />\n傻既都pass，咁你就係依7日同新入職果d人互相識下。<br />\n<br />\n係暑假前個時好多後生貪心鮮入去，都有唔少女仔架。<br />\n<br />\n不過入面好多怪人（能人異士？），自己好運。<br />\n<br />\n自問自己夠垃圾夠廢既未入去做下lo，<br />\n<br />\n不過同成班廢人一齊團火好快熄，<br />\n<br />\n會一直廢落去loop到死為止。<br />\n<br />\n分3更，9碼都辛苦死你，你頂到未12碼lo。<br />\n<br />\n總結，廢人工一份，番依份工會令自己都養唔掂自己。"},{"pid":"56d778c142a8ffcee39ea5bd4494ce516e70fd99","tid":54081,"uid":15552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T03:33:53.000Z","msg":"升3柴要升幾耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb1593e8cdcdd2db060aebe925b6f1bae9807347","tid":54081,"uid":51932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T03:47:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>升3柴要升幾耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n擦鞋叻唔叻先，某部門有個隊長上3再升4，快到呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c12867fa04e3623f7fa8f83cad5946f219918b36","tid":54081,"uid":51932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T03:49:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>