風<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n機場撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"803d8a3e46b761364120594a921d6b819c6b678d","tid":54081,"uid":38145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T06:24:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>In個時係咪可以比你揀部門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 小弟想做check旅客行理部安檢查應該係咩部門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n上完佢既堂就有得揀<br />\n<br />\n靚仔後生就做前線 做門口狗 check手提行李<br />\n柒頭毒撚老野就守禁區睇機坪 睇寄倉行李<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不成文既規定好似係"},{"pid":"959a302186b07db77c4da2d34ce41acd8fba083a","tid":54081,"uid":15199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T06:25:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>多唔多靚女做<br />\n見極 都係美極 同埋驅風<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n機場撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔多<br />\n靚果d 都一早比人食哂"},{"pid":"6b3def8d4981b7c997e639315c5ceaf52f7b19f8","tid":54081,"uid":46086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T06:25:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>升3柴要升幾耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n擦鞋叻唔叻先，某部門有個隊長上3再升4，快到呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n邊撚個唔係上3再升4架？ 直接2升4呀？"},{"pid":"db90a1b6c54c0af956e6917404b3e02b5d12ed08","tid":54081,"uid":5016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T06:31:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> TRA 看更一名<br />\n日日食坐食坐 做到人到頹哂<br />\n萬幾蚊會搞到你冇工作以外既朋友冇人生意義<br />\n因為要輪更 嗰排個樣都OK殘 黑眼圈 <br />\n成日唔夠瞓<br />\n但就都叫做儲到下錢既<br />\n做唔做真係你諗你啦<br />\n<br />\n利申 已經遞左信冇做</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n屌你我都遞左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9962186e0a80ce43351663e7a19f9fffae5d1771","tid":54081,"uid":62424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T06:33:17.000Z","msg":"做咩部門"},{"